This is a Java library used to interface with the data glove 
manufactured by Fifth Dimension Technologies, http://www.5dt.com/.

To use this library, you will need the shared libraries from 5DT. 
Download them here,
  http://www.5dt.com/downloads.html#oldglove

Type "make" at the shell prompt to build the library.

Type "make doc" at the shell prompt to build the documentation for the library.

Refer to the HTML files in the "doc" directory for information on how to 
use the JNI library.


